New in this build:

• Import runs from your watch via Health Connect — pull in runs recorded on your Garmin, Amazfit or other watch, even when you leave your phone at home.
• Heart rate, distance and elevation sync into each run automatically.
• New training styles — balanced, polarized, run/walk, low-frequency or Hansons — and your plan rebuilds around your pick.
• Smoother race discovery and stability fixes.

Thanks for testing! Please report anything that breaks.
